            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@Apurv You don&apos;t want to &quot;soften consequences&quot;, you want to do everything possible to protect against it. To be fair though, setting the correct user access is important, but not really what the OP is asking for.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/519924/alexander-holsgrove&quot; title=&quot;1,735 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Alexander Holsgrove&lt;/a&gt;
