            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I think the whole point of the question is to get this done without using such framework.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/3910951/sanke&quot; title=&quot;524 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Sanke&lt;/a&gt;
